data.value: Placing an order on BigDeal is easy! Simply browse our collection of clothing and other fashion items, add your desired items to the cart, and proceed to checkout. Follow the prompts to enter your shipping and payment details, and your order will be on its way.

data.name: label17.Text
data.value: We want you to be completely satisfied with your purchase. If for any reason you're not happy with your order, you can return it within 7 days for a full refund or exchange, subject to our return policy.
